{"tid":664060,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Chris Evans接拍《District 9》導演災難新片《Greenland》","createTime":"2018-05-13T19:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T02:55:27.000Z","uid":66943,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f3841335e64a50f8f6f73471d4ee560cd2283764","tid":664060,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T19:28:09.000Z","msg":"據DeadlineHollywood報導，&ldquo;Captain&rdquo; Chris Evans確認將主演《District 9》導演Neill Blomkamp的新片《Greenland》。本片為災難驚悚題材，講述了一個家庭對抗災難性自然災害的故事，電影預計在2018年最後一個季度開拍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180513_wyc_246_10/gamersky_02origin_03_20185131654A5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180513_wyc_246_10%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_20185131654A5F.jpg&h=f0f8f372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據發行方STXinternational介紹，《Greenland》是一部高度商業化的電影作品，它可以讓導Neill Blomkamp發揮自己的特長，在一個人們所熟知的世界中帶來極具概念性和創意的故事。<br />\n<br />\n　　Neill Blomkamp曾執導過《District 9》、《Elysium》和《Chappie》等極具特色的科幻電影，雖然從介紹中來看《Greenland》與自然災害相關，不會有多少科幻元素存在，但由Neill Blomkamp執導，我們或許可以期待一下能看到更多新奇的元素。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180513_wyc_246_10/gamersky_01origin_01_2018513165449B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180513_wyc_246_10%2Fgamersky_01origin_01_2018513165449B.jpg&h=a66f9b16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2cd3691786af6df5435c931369f1f1dc0050f4d","tid":664060,"uid":18569,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T23:56:56.000Z","msg":"3年又3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝦仔幾時有續集"},{"pid":"2a037bf8e2ddf4faa332252e1faea4dfd4ca6912","tid":664060,"uid":135867,"like":10,"dislike":23,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:02:26.000Z","msg":"除左Captain，佢做戲真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6388fafd0df6aeef1c30004207cdadeb0cab0b7